Class DefaultTicketSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.unicon.cas.addons.ticket.internal.DefaultTicketSupport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TicketSupport

    @Component
public class DefaultTicketSupport
extends Object
implements TicketSupport
    Default implementation of TicketSupport

    Uses CAS' TicketRegistry to retrieve TGT and its associated objects by provided tgt String token

    Since:
    1.0.3
    Author:
    Dmitriy Kopylenko, Unicon, inc.
